{"tid":2117041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［廣傳］功能組別提名要人，只剩十日，不要功虧一簣！","createTime":"2020-07-20T14:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T08:37:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2589bbade767aaaf90ff7fa623801fcbe7cb0e66","tid":2117041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"攬炒藝術家2020/7/20 <br />\n<br />\n區選大勝，首先因為有素人「填白區」參選，盡力阻止親共派自動當選。功能組別如今也有人想「填白區」阻止自動當選，奈何由於選民分散，爭取提名也有一定難度，雖然只需十人提名，但就算搞街站也不會那麼容易撞正該界別的已登記選民。我呼籲大家廣傳，俾功能組別的已登記選民幫手，到以下 TG 協助提名相關界別：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/businessfrontier\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbusinessfrontier&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=482c8ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/businessfrontier</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/legcodiscuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flegcodiscuss&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=f0d14ad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/legcodiscuss</a><br />\n<br />\n較需要提名的有：<br />\n<br />\n進出口界<br />\n商界(第一) (登記選民的條件為香港總商會公司會員滿一年)<br />\n工業界(第一) (登記選民的條件為香港工業總會公司會員滿一年，貿易業/工業支援除外)<br />\n紡織及製衣界<br />\n保險界 (登記選民的條件為持牌保險公司運作滿一年)<br />\n其他界別想提名的選民亦可入以上 TG。<br />\n<br />\n這些連提名也難攞的界別泛民普遍看淡，但正如素人參選的區議會，本來亦被看淡，起碼有人落場參選就仲有機會。退而求其次，亦可取得票數數據方便部署明年的特首選委選戰。<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%BA-%E5%8F%AA%E5%89%A9%E5%8D%81%E6%97%A5-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%99%A7%E4%B8%80%E7%B0%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%2589%25A9%25E5%258D%2581%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2599%25A7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25B0%25A3%2F&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=2dad0e4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%2589%25A9%25E5%258D%2581%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2599%25A7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25B0%25A3%2F&h=29bc9a40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%BA-%E5%8F%AA%E5%89%A9%E5%8D%81%E6%97%A5-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%99%A7%E4%B8%80%E7%B0%A3/</a>"},{"pid":"d603e70602513454bdf714920f3e6383bc3328c2","tid":2117041,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005dc069a3c8627df18e9e0dca45402ca4f9b0d8","tid":2117041,"uid":175125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:06:01.000Z","msg":"究竟進出口界有冇人選<br />\n冇人選點提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5770d7292996cf74b932740cb89b4bfbe42d681e","tid":2117041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"005dc069a3c8627df18e9e0dca45402ca4f9b0d8","tid":2117041,"uid":175125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:06:01.000Z","msg":"究竟進出口界有冇人選<br />\n冇人選點提名<img src=\"/assets